that sailed from European waters.

00:07:10.530 --> 00:07:14.760
China has a deep and abiding
history in the Pacific

00:07:14.760 --> 00:07:21.660
and that relationship, the maritime
reach of the United States balanced

00:07:21.660 --> 00:07:26.810
with China's ancient sense
of itself as a Pacific power,

00:07:26.810 --> 00:07:29.280
is truly the light motif that plays

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:33.300
in the geopolitics
of the Pacific today.

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:36.180
And we see the Chinese Navy rising.

00:07:36.180 --> 00:07:37.480
It is reaching out.

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:38.780
It is deploying.

00:07:38.780 --> 00:07:41.340
Here's a Chinese Corvette arriving

00:07:41.340 --> 00:07:46.730
