Pearl Harbor, Hawaii.

00:07:46.730 --> 00:07:52.960 position:56%
China is also brining its allies and
coalition partners into the Pacific.

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:59.780
This is a Chinese destroyer
operating with a Russian destroyer.

00:07:59.780 --> 00:08:04.420
Now, the United States has
terrific allies in the Pacific.

00:08:04.420 --> 00:08:08.780
This is also part of
our relationship set.

00:08:08.780 --> 00:08:11.720
This is Prime Minister Shinzo Abe,

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.430
[assumed spelling]
a reliable partner

00:08:13.430 --> 00:08:19.120
