professional and capable.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:25.630
We also have excellent partners on
the Korean peninsula, South Korea.

00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:31.350
Together we have a challenge
that is, in many ways, maritime.

00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:32.780
It's from North Korea.

00:08:32.780 --> 00:08:35.390
This of course is Kim Jung Un,

00:08:35.390 --> 00:08:36.690
[assumed spelling]
and he is well named.

00:08:36.690 --> 00:08:38.780
He is unpredictable.

00:08:38.780 --> 00:08:42.580
He's unstable.

00:08:42.580 --> 00:08:45.130
He's not irrational.

00:08:45.130 --> 00:08:47.000
He's got a really bad haircut.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:52.520
[laughter] And the bad news is
