00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:37.760
China's construction of artificial
islands in the Pacific today --

00:09:37.760 --> 00:09:39.160
the Western Pacific --

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:42.740
we see significant
geopolitical competition.

00:09:42.740 --> 00:09:44.980
Let's keep moving.

00:09:44.980 --> 00:09:48.170
Let's go to the Atlantic,
