00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:01.670
Not insurmountable, not
leading to another war,

00:11:01.670 --> 00:11:06.150
but tension that will play
out in this maritime sphere

00:11:06.150 --> 00:11:11.440
as we see Russian frontline
ships operating as here

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:15.030
in the Caribbean off our coast.

00:11:15.030 --> 00:11:16.330
Let's move on.

00:11:16.330 --> 00:11:22.470
The third largest ocean, after the
Pacific and the Atlantic, is this;

00:11:22.470 --> 00:11:26.910
the Indian Ocean, which begins
to hit the world's stage

00:11:26.910 --> 00:11:29.820
