in this century -- with Pakistan.

00:11:45.580 --> 00:11:48.410
That will, over the
course of this century,

00:11:48.410 --> 00:11:52.350
drive geopolitics in
the Indian Ocean.

00:11:52.350 --> 00:11:57.910
We see it today tactically in
Yemen, in the northern reaches

00:11:57.910 --> 00:12:03.680
of the Indian Ocean, and up into
the Persian Gulf, where the overlay

00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:10.160
of Shia -- that's the Iranian
flag, upper right -- Sunni --

00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:12.980
that's the Saudi flag,
bottom left --

00:12:12.980 --> 00:12:16.330
