around that Arabian Peninsula

00:12:16.330 --> 00:12:19.810
with our greatest ally
in the region, Israel,

00:12:19.810 --> 00:12:21.990
parked in the middle of that zone.

00:12:21.990 --> 00:12:25.710
So the geopolitical
challenges here will continue.

00:12:25.710 --> 00:12:33.940
And of course we need to recall
