00:12:51.030 --> 00:12:54.090
Note all of the coastline here.

00:12:54.090 --> 00:12:58.180
Again, we will see
geopolitics playing out in

00:12:58.180 --> 00:12:59.670
that Indian Ocean as well.

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:04.550
Let's go to the Mediterranean
Sea, where many of you have sailed

00:13:04.550 --> 00:13:08.420
on very benign cruises I
imagine, in the summer.

00:13:08.420 --> 00:13:12.030
My wife and I did a
wonderful one two summers ago.

00:13:12.030 --> 00:13:16.050
But let me tell you something very
somber about the Mediterranean Sea.

00:13:16.050 --> 00:13:20.190
If I could snap my fingers
[snap] and bring back

00:13:20.190 --> 00:13:25.810
to life every sunken warship
and every mariner who died

00:13:25.810 --> 00:13:29.690
in maritime combat in
the Mediterranean Sea,

00:13:29.690 --> 00:13:32.630
you could walk across that ocean.

00:13:32.630 --> 00:13:35.450
It is an enormous zone of war.

00:13:35.450 --> 00:13:39.870 position:56%
A highlight battle, if you will, if
there's such a thing, was the Battle

00:13:39.870 --> 00:13:47.940
of Lepanto, the high-water mark of
Islamic drive in the seas off Italy

00:13:47.940 --> 00:13:51.930
against the Holy Roman
Empire in the 1570s.

00:13:51.930 --> 00:13:54.010
What's the situation today?

00:13:54.010 --> 00:13:59.610 position:56%
It's the Eastern Mediterranean where
we see geopolitics most at play.

00:13:59.610 --> 00:14:02.220
We see great powers, the
United States and Russia,

00:14:02.220 --> 00:14:06.090
on opposite sides in
the conflicted Syria.

00:14:06.090 --> 00:14:10.280
We see enormous turbulence
throughout the Levant and it leads

00:14:10.280 --> 00:14:15.990
to this, a maritime
challenge; two million refugees

00:14:15.990 --> 00:14:17.850
over the last three years.

00:14:17.850 --> 00:14:23.220
This Eastern Mediterranean
will be a zone of challenge,

00:14:23.220 --> 00:14:26.480
if not conflict --
and also because under

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:30.380
that Eastern Mediterranean
is an enormous treasure trove

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:33.570
of hydrocarbons --
oil, natural gas --

00:14:33.570 --> 00:14:36.860
disputed among the
nations in that region.

00:14:36.860 --> 00:14:40.120
So the Mediterranean will
challenge us as well.

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:41.730
Let's come a little closer to home.

00:14:41.730 --> 00:14:47.190
The Caribbean Sea was
