the case under international law

00:36:35.550 --> 00:36:38.540
in the United Nations
Convention on the Law of the Sea

00:36:38.540 --> 00:36:44.660
that we are observing and enforcing
customary international law

00:36:44.660 --> 00:36:47.080
as described by the
International Courts.

00:36:47.080 --> 00:36:48.750
I think if we stay in the game

00:36:48.750 --> 00:36:54.290
